ub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"übersicht","title":"Übersicht","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das <em>HTML Strikethrough Element</em> (<code>&lt;s&gt;</code>) stellt Text mit einer durchgestrichenen Linie dar. Benutzt wird das <code>&lt;s&gt;</code> Element um zu repräsentieren, dass Dinge nicht länger relevant oder zutreffend sind. <code>&lt;s&gt;</code> ist jedoch nicht dafür geeignet, um Dokumentenänderungen anzuzeigen - hierfür sollten das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/del\"><code>&lt;del&gt;</code></a> und das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ins\"><code>&lt;ins&gt;</code></a> Element genutzt werden.</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Inhaltskategorien</a></th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Phrasing content\">Formulierungsinhalt</a> oder <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">fließender Inhalt</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubter Inhalt</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#transparent\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Transparent\">Transparent</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Tag Auslassung</th>\n   <td>Keine, sowohl das Anfangs- als auch das End-Tag sind erforderlich.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">Erlaubte Elternelemente</th>\n   <td>Jedes Element, dass <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\">Formulierungsinhalt</a> erlaubt.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">DOM Schnittstelle</th>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Dieses Element schließt nur </span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">globale Attribute</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\"> ein.</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_schnittstelle","title":"DOM Schnittstelle","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element implementiert die <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element\" title=\"DOM/element\">HTMLElement</a></code> Schnittstelle.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\"><strong>Hinweis zur Implementierung: </strong>Bis einschließlich Gecko 1.9.2, hat Firefox die <a href=\"/en-US/docs/DOM/span\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code></a> Schnittstelle für dieses Element implementiert.</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>s</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Heute im Angebot: Lachs<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>s</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> AUSVERKAUFT<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>br</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token special-attr\"><span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span><span class=\"token value css language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">text-decoration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>line-through<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Heute im Angebot: Lachs<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> AUSVERKAUFT</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ergebnis","title":"Ergebnis","isH3":true,"content":"<p><s>Heute im Angebot: Lachs</s> AUSVERKAUFT<br>\n <s style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">Heute im Angebot: Lachs</s> AUSVERKAUFT</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Das <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Element, der Vorgänger des <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/s\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;s&gt;</code></a> Elements ist veraltet und sollte nicht mehr genutzt werden.</li>\n <li>Das <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/del\"><code>&lt;del&gt;</code></a> Element, welches genutzt werden sollte, wenn Daten <em>gelöscht</em> wurden.</li>\n <li>Die CSS <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/text-decoration\"><code>text-decoration</code></a> Eigenschaft um die visuellen Aspekte des <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/s\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>&lt;s&gt;</code></a> Elements zu archivieren.</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Übersicht","id":"übersicht"},{"text":"Attribute","id":"attribute"},{"text":"DOM Schnittstelle","id":"dom_schnittstelle"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Das HTML Strikethrough Element (<s>) stellt Text mit einer durchgestrichenen Linie dar. Benutzt wird das <s> Element um zu repräsentieren, dass Dinge nicht länger relevant oder zutreffend sind. <s> ist jedoch nicht dafür geeignet, um Dokumentenänderungen anzuzeigen - hierfür sollten das <del> und das <ins> Element genutzt werden.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<s>: The Strikethrough element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"s","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<s>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<s>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<s>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"s","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"<s>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<s>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/s","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/s/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/s","title":"<s>"}],"pageTitle":"<s> - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}